{"tid":1307186,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗新田「信芯園」園主梁日信以成本價向治喪委員會提供2千支用作悼念的向日葵","createTime":"2019-07-11T12:40:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T13:32:18.000Z","uid":240362,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a335ef258a68467fb35468987fd014f040d6b7ab","tid":1307186,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T12:40:49.000Z","msg":"【逆權運動】風雨不減思念情 千支向日葵伴杰仔上路<br />\n<br />\n現場2千支用作悼念的向日葵，是由元朗新田「信芯園」園主梁日信（信哥）以成本價向治喪委員會提供，信哥指1966年時只有10歲的他，已曾參加被稱為「123事件」的澳門史上最大規模反對澳葡政府示威。信哥直言自己已年逾60，難再有年輕人的精力去抗爭，故惟有出一分力量提供鮮花，也希望學生能和平地達到理想。對於有抗爭者輕生，信哥指非常難過，希望特首能盡快與年青人溝通。"},{"pid":"cec6fa98d6d135bad446db8e7de3e442579fb254","tid":1307186,"uid":39698,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T12:48:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6d412a5bd5ce4690b310b29d0043eefe467ced8","tid":1307186,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T13:28:26.000Z","msg":"2千支<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21fb72b90d2aca17247604a439e8a04a4977e3d6","tid":1307186,"uid":997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T13:32:18.000Z","msg":"不如del post啦,唔好搞到人"}]}